{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/posts/posts/writing-guide/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soohy00"}},"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"1. Add a post You can add posts by creating a new markdown document in the contents/post path. 1-1. Post file structure There are two waysâ€¦","html":"<h2>1. Add a post</h2>\n<p>You can add posts by creating a new markdown document in the <code>contents/post</code> path.</p>\n<h3>1-1. Post file structure</h3>\n<p>There are two ways to add a new document. The first is to create a markdown file for a single document without a directory. If you are writing about JavaScript, you can create a <code>about-javascript.md</code> file in the <code>contents/posts</code> directory.</p>\n<p>The second is to create a directory and create an <code>index.md</code> file in it. This method is useful when the document contains several additional files such as picture files.</p>\n<p>Each file name or directory name becomes a unique address of the document and can be accessed as follows. <code>https://siteURL/about-javascript</code>.</p>\n<h3>1-2. Frontmatter</h3>\n<p>The Markdown document you create contains the document's metadata called frontmatter.</p>\n<pre><code>---\ntitle: \"ðŸ¤” 3. Writing Guide\"\ndescription: \"How to write and add a post?\"\ndate: 2021-05-03\nupdate: 2021-05-03\ntags:\n  - hoodie\n  - writing-guide\nseries: \"Getting started your blog with gatsby-starter-hoodie\"\n---\n</code></pre>\n<p>Above is the frontmatter of the document you are currently reading. Among them, title and date are required. It is recommended to enclose the string with spaces in quotation marks.</p>\n<h3>1-3. Writing markdown</h3>\n<p>If you have written a Frontmatter, you can write your markdown document under it. gatsby-starter-hoodie supports most Markdown syntax. To learn more about Markdown syntax, see the Mastering Markdown<sup id=\"fnref-1\"><a href=\"#fn-1\" class=\"footnote-ref\">1</a></sup> documentation on GitHub.</p>\n<h2>2. Syntax Highlighting &#x26; Katex</h2>\n<h3>2-1. Syntax Highlighting</h3>\n<p>Syntax highlighting based on Prism.JS is supported.</p>\n<h4>Examples</h4>\n<p>Javascript</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">console.log(\"Hello, world!\")\n</code></pre>\n<p>Python</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">print(\"Hello, world!\")\n</code></pre>\n<p>It supports a wider variety of other languages. Check it out on the <a href=\"https://prismjs.com/\">Prism.js website</a>.</p>\n<h3>2-2. Katex</h3>\n<p>It supports Katex syntax, you can easily express complex formulas.</p>\n<h4>Inline mode</h4>\n<p>$$E = m c^{2}$$</p>\n<h4>Block mode</h4>\n<p>$$\n\\int_{0}^{\\infty} f(x) dx\n$$</p>\n<h2>3. Add images to a post</h2>\n<p>You can easily embed images using relative paths. It is easy to manage documents containing images by creating a directory.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/cb58d/sample-image.webp 300w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/f8b1b/sample-image.webp 600w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/5bb53/sample-image.webp 1200w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/8fb31/sample-image.webp 1800w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/7e36f/sample-image.webp 1920w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/37e03/sample-image.jpg 300w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/2a8be/sample-image.jpg 600w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/5a523/sample-image.jpg 1200w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/96503/sample-image.jpg 1800w,\n/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/69b48/sample-image.jpg 1920w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/69b244095d8c72158c9dd2d4ca59a7b1/5a523/sample-image.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Sample Image Caption\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Images are loaded with Lazy Loading, so you can secure fast document loading speed.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>âš  The extension of the file must be set to lowercase.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>4. Tagging</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 737px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.999999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/cb58d/tag-example.webp 300w,\n/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/f8b1b/tag-example.webp 600w,\n/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/89432/tag-example.webp 737w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 737px) 100vw, 737px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/37e03/tag-example.jpg 300w,\n/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/2a8be/tag-example.jpg 600w,\n/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/3dbaa/tag-example.jpg 737w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 737px) 100vw, 737px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/82ce4bec7f5360eef32a473171b181af/3dbaa/tag-example.jpg\"\n            alt=\"tag example\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can classify and search documents by tag set in Frontmatter. All tags you set can be viewed and searched in <code>https://siteUrl/tags</code>.</p>\n<h2>5. Series</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 677px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/cb58d/series-example.webp 300w,\n/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/f8b1b/series-example.webp 600w,\n/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/90928/series-example.webp 677w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 677px) 100vw, 677px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/37e03/series-example.jpg 300w,\n/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/2a8be/series-example.jpg 600w,\n/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/5a211/series-example.jpg 677w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 677px) 100vw, 677px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1ea4e56966cb5fb6e110d32124fd883c/5a211/series-example.jpg\"\n            alt=\"series example\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can publish multiple related documents in a series. The series set in Frontmatter is grouped together and shown at the top of the document. This can be useful for serialized documents with an order. Series documents are displayed in ascending order of creation date.</p>\n<p>The current document is also set in a series called <code>Getting started your blog with gatsby-starter-hoodie</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"footnotes\">\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li id=\"fn-1\"><a href=\"https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/\">https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/</a><a href=\"#fnref-1\" class=\"footnote-backref\">â†©</a></li>\n</ol>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"ðŸ¤” 3. Writing Guide","date":"May 03, 2021","tags":["about"],"series":"Getting started your blog with gatsby-starter-hoodie"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/posts/writing-guide/"}},"seriesList":{"nodes":[{"id":"5c2c6aa4-fe8e-5e17-945e-5ab9f0cecf7b","fields":{"slug":"/posts/posts/quick-start/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ðŸš€ 2. Quick Start","date":"May 02, 2021"}},{"id":"c68f14ed-3820-5f33-a0bb-9211ebca812f","fields":{"slug":"/posts/posts/writing-guide/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ðŸ¤” 3. Writing Guide","date":"May 03, 2021"}}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"c68f14ed-3820-5f33-a0bb-9211ebca812f","slug":"/posts/posts/writing-guide/","series":"Getting started your blog with gatsby-starter-hoodie","previousPostId":"ea49ea48-d8e1-5857-8373-bfb3105bf3df","nextPostId":"5c2c6aa4-fe8e-5e17-945e-5ab9f0cecf7b"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}